{"word":"G5387 - φιλόστοργος - philóstorgos - fil-os'-tor-gos - Kindly affectioned","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φιλόστοργος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">philóstorgos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">fil-os'-tor-gos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Kindly affectioned</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பட்சமாயிருக்கிற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"loving affection, prone to love, loving tenderly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5384 - φίλος - phílos - fee'-los/5384\">G5384</a> and <b>&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03BF;&#x03C1;&#x03B3;&#x03B7;&#x0301;</b> s<b>torge&#x0304;</b> (<i>cherishing</i> one&rsquo;s kindred, especially parents or children); <i>fond of</i> natural <i>relatives</i>, that is, <i>fraternal</i> towards fellow Christians: - kindly affectioned.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2705/2705\">G2705</a>, <a href=\"#/G5367/5367\">G5367</a>, <a href=\"#/G5368/5368\">G5368</a>, <a href=\"#/G5369/5369\">G5369</a>, <a href=\"#/G5370/5370\">G5370</a>, <a href=\"#/G5373/5373\">G5373</a>, <a href=\"#/G5377/5377\">G5377</a>, <a href=\"#/G5383/5383\">G5383</a>, <a href=\"#/G5384/5384\">G5384</a>, <a href=\"#/G5387/5387\">G5387</a>"}]}